---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout title="Bienvenido al equipo">
  <Nav current="/" />

  <header class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <p class="label">info.getkore.es — Documento interno</p>
      <h1>
        <span data-es>El smartphone<br/><em>que es tuyo</em><br/>de verdad.</span>
        <span data-en>The smartphone<br/><em>that is truly</em><br/>yours.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="sub" data-es>Esta web recoge todo lo que necesitas saber sobre Kore:<br/>filosofía, producto, estrategia y visión de equipo.</p>
      <p class="sub" data-en>This site covers everything you need to know about Kore:<br/>philosophy, product, strategy and team vision.</p>
      <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="num amber">1,000</span>
          <span class="lbl" data-es>Unidades totales</span>
          <span class="lbl" data-en>Total units</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="num">7</span>
          <span class="lbl" data-es>Años de actualizaciones</span>
          <span class="lbl" data-en>Years of updates</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="num">0</span>
          <span class="lbl" data-es>Datos enviados</span>
          <span class="lbl" data-en>Data sent</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="num amber">€2,499</span>
          <span class="lbl" data-es>Desde</span>
          <span class="lbl" data-en>Starting from</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="section">
    <p class="label" style="margin-bottom:48px">
      <span data-es>Navega por las secciones</span>
      <span data-en>Browse sections</span>
    </p>
    <div class="grid">

      <a href="/empresa" class="card">
        <span class="card-num label">01</span>
        <h2 data-es>La Empresa</h2>
        <h2 data-en>The Company</h2>
        <p data-es>Quiénes somos, por qué existimos y qué nos hace diferentes desde la base.</p>
        <p data-en>Who we are, why we exist and what makes us different from the ground up.</p>
        <span class="card-link amber" data-es>Ver más →</span>
        <span class="card-link amber" data-en>Read more →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/filosofia" class="card">
        <span class="card-num label">02</span>
        <h2 data-es>Filosofía</h2>
        <h2 data-en>Philosophy</h2>
        <p data-es>Los principios que guían cada decisión de diseño, producto y negocio.</p>
        <p data-en>The principles guiding every design, product and business decision.</p>
        <span class="card-link amber" data-es>Ver más →</span>
        <span class="card-link amber" data-en>Read more →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/manifiesto" class="card">
        <span class="card-num label">03</span>
        <h2>Manifesto</h2>
        <p data-es>El texto fundacional de Kore. Por qué el smartphone actual no es tuyo y qué hacemos al respecto.</p>
        <p data-en>Kore's founding text. Why your current smartphone isn't really yours — and what we do about it.</p>
        <span class="card-link amber" data-es>Ver más →</span>
        <span class="card-link amber" data-en>Read more →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/inscripcion" class="card">
        <span class="card-num label">04</span>
        <h2 data-es>Página de Inscripción</h2>
        <h2 data-en>Signup Page</h2>
        <p data-es>La landing de lista de espera con el flujo completo de email de bienvenida.</p>
        <p data-en>The waitlist landing page with the full welcome email flow.</p>
        <span class="card-link amber" data-es>Ver más →</span>
        <span class="card-link amber" data-en>Read more →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/estrategia" class="card">
        <span class="card-num label">05</span>
        <h2 data-es>Estrategia de Lanzamiento</h2>
        <h2 data-en>Launch Strategy</h2>
        <p data-es>Plan de 6 meses: canales, audiencias, hitos y métricas de éxito.</p>
        <p data-en>6-month plan: channels, audiences, milestones and success metrics.</p>
        <span class="card-link amber" data-es>Ver más →</span>
        <span class="card-link amber" data-en>Read more →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/vs-competencia" class="card">
        <span class="card-num label">06</span>
        <h2 data-es>Kore vs. Competencia</h2>
        <h2 data-en>Kore vs. Competition</h2>
        <p data-es>Por qué Kore gana donde Apple, Samsung y otros no pueden seguirte.</p>
        <p data-en>Why Kore wins where Apple, Samsung and others simply cannot follow.</p>
        <span class="card-link amber" data-es>Ver más →</span>
        <span class="card-link amber" data-en>Read more →</span>
      </a>

    </div>

    <div class="quote-block">
      <blockquote data-es>
        "No es el más barato. No tiene el ecosistema más grande.<br/>
        Pero es el único que, cuando lo compras, es completamente tuyo."
      </blockquote>
      <blockquote data-en>
        "It's not the cheapest. It doesn't have the biggest ecosystem.<br/>
        But it's the only one that, when you buy it, is completely yours."
      </blockquote>
      <cite class="label">— Kore Manifesto</cite>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 50% 50%, rgba(200,169,110,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.1);
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 120px 48px 80px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hero-inner .label { margin-bottom: 32px; }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(52px, 8vw, 100px);
    line-height: 1.0;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    color: var(--ivory);
  }

  h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--amber); }

  .sub {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--titanium-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.15);
  }

  .stat {
    padding: 24px 20px;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.1);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .stat:last-child { border-right: none; }

  .num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--ivory);
  }

  .lbl {
    font-size: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--titanium);
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--carbon);
    padding: 40px 32px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(200,169,110,0.3);
    background: rgba(200,169,110,0.04);
  }

  .card-num { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .card h2 { font-size: 26px; color: var(--ivory); }
  .card p { font-size: 11px; color: var(--titanium); line-height: 1.8; flex: 1; }
  .card-link { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; margin-top: 8px; }

  .quote-block {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--amber);
    padding: 32px 40px;
    background: var(--carbon);
    margin-top: 80px;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ivory);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-inner { padding: 100px 24px 60px; }
  }
</style>
